Shredder raises an eyebrow as Bobertron jumps in front of him, taking the 
shots. That was strange. Shredder glances at Bobertron's unconcious body 
before lookng back at Wrath.

Shredder keeps firing at Wrath. The sooner the dang bot retreated the sooner 
Shredder could go back to dealing with Megatron and looking over Magmatron's 
proposal. Or maybe getting Bobertron to a CR tank.
